videos.headline: Lawrence keeps it himself for first Clemson TD of season
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence fakes the handoff and runs in for a two-yard Clemson touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lawrence keeps it himself for first Clemson TD of season) 2020/9/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lawrence rushes in for second TD
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence fakes the handoff again and breaks the plane on his own to put Clemson ahead of Wake Forest 14-0.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lawrence rushes in for second TD) 2020/9/12 ESHEET
